description:
Luffy and Sanji make a bold trek up a snow-covered mountain in search of a witch who might hold the key to curing Nami.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: An Island Without Doctors? Adventure in a Nameless Land!

医者のいない島? 名も無き国の冒険!
